"      Roussos C, Macklem PT. The respiratory muscles. N Engl J Med 1982; 307:786.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/15/14584/abstract/2\">",
"      Fell SC. Surgical anatomy of the diaphragm and the phrenic nerve. Chest Surg Clin N Am 1998; 8:281.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?14/15/14584/abstract/3\">",
"      Rochester DF. The diaphragm: contractile properties and fatigue. J Clin Invest 1985; 75:1397.",
"     </a>",
